thread.title: Angela Larsen

author: Angela Larsen
title: Angela Larsen
text: Without a doubt, the best customer service ever! The Manager, Manny (Key West), worked with us to ensure we rented the most appropriate space for our needs, at a very reasonable cost. As a former customer service Executive, I was impressed as to the courtesy, professionalism and knowledge of this individual. Storage Mart is very fortunate to have such an excellent representative on its team!
